===Background===
[[File:Slaughter.png|thumb|left|Aegon is killed by Gregor Clegane]]Aegon Targaryen was the son of Prince Rhaegar Targaryen and [[Elia Martell]]. He had an older sister, [[Rhaenys Targaryen (daughter of Rhaegar)|Rhaenys Targaryen]].&lt;ref&gt;[http://viewers-guide.hbo.com/game-of-thrones/#!/guide/houses/targaryen/ HBO Viewers Guide House Targaryen Family Tree]&lt;/ref&gt; [[House Targaryen]] was deposed as the ruling house of [[Westeros]] during [[Robert's Rebellion]]. Rhaegar was killed during the fighting and Elia and both their children were killed soon afterwards during the [[Sack of King's Landing]].&lt;ref name=&quot;Elia viewers guide&quot;&gt;[http://viewers-guide.hbo.com/game-ofthrones/season2/#!/guide/houses/targaryen/elia-targaryen/ HBO viewers guide, season 2 guide to houses, House Targaryen - Elia Targaryen entry]&lt;/ref&gt;

Had he lived and ascended the throne, he would have ruled as &quot;Aegon VI&quot;.
